    "summary": "The user presents symptoms of a potential ankle fracture (deformity, inability to bear weight, severe swelling). The assistant initially offers standard advice but quickly descends into nonsensical, hallucinatory gibberish, ultimately telling the user to skip doctors and X-rays in favor of \"tea, sunshine,\" and a fictional character named \"Scramchi.\"",
